HTTP error: 400 Bad Request - Failed to execute query: Internal error: User function 'text_search' is called on table 'qs' that has 2 full text search columns. Must call 'text_search' with column parameter, e.g. `text_search("my table", 'my query', my_search_col)`..
This was likely caused by a bug in DataFusion's code and we would welcome that you file an bug report in our issue tracker
